main event: A UFO sighting reported on 23 June 1965 in Trenton, Missouri, involving a bright object that appeared to follow a couple returning home.
interesting points: Mr. and Mrs. Guat Sanchez observed the object for 20-25 minutes,The object was round and about 30 feet in diameter, emitting a bright white light,Neighbors confirmed the sighting and described similar movements of the object,The object hovered and made sudden movements in different directions before disappearing at a high rate of speed,The observation coincided with an explanation from the Air Force suggesting it may have been a refraction of the rising sun.
sighted object: a bright white round object in the sky
witness description: Mr. and Mrs. Guat Sanchez and neighbors
